#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:292
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"\\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Walls protection}{Protection} from \\svg[15]{unit_ranged} Attacks}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{2}\n"
"\\subsection*{\\pagetarget{Walls protection}{Ochrona} przed Atakami \\svg[15]{unit_ranged}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:296
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Defending units standing on their own side and \\textbf{in the same column} as a non-destroyed Wall or Gate gain protection from \\svg{unit_ranged} attacks.\n"
"If they are targeted by a \\svg{unit_ranged} attack performed from the opponent's side of the Combat Board, \\textbf{reduce the attack's damage by 1}.\n"
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Broniące jednostki stojące po swojej stronie i~\\textbf{w~tej samej kolumnie} co niezniszczony Mur lub Brama otrzymują ochronę przed atakami \\svg{unit_ranged}.\n"
"Jeśli są celem ataku \\svg{unit_ranged} wykonanego z~przeciwnej strony Planszy Walki, \\textbf{zmniejsz obrażenia tego ataku o~1}.\n"
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:300
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  \\transparent{0.15}\\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\art/lions_shield_of_courage.png}\n"
"\\end{center}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  \\transparent{0.15}\\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\art/lions_shield_of_courage.png}\n"
"\\end{center}"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:308
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\examples/ranged_protected.png}\n"
"{\\textit{When the Halberdiers are behind a non-destroyed Gate, they \\textbf{are protected} when attacked from the opponent's side of the Combat Board.\n"
"  The \\svg{unit_ranged} attack damage of Evil Eyes is \\textbf{reduced by 1}.}}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{2}\n"
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\examples/ranged_protected.png}\n"
"{\\textit{Gdy Halabardnicy znajdują się za niezniszczoną Bramą, \\textbf{są chronieni} przed atakami z~przeciwnej strony Planszy Walki.\n"
"  Obrażenia ataku \\svg{unit_ranged} Złych Oczu są \\textbf{zmniejszone o~1}.}}\n"
"\\newline\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/combat.tex:314
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\examples/ranged_unprotected.png}\n"
"{\\textit{Because the Halberdiers are not behind a non-destroyed Wall, \\textbf{protection doesn't work}.\n"
"  Evil Eyes attack \\textbf{without penalty}.}}\n"
"\\newline\\newline"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\examples/ranged_unprotected.png}\n"
"{\\textit{Ponieważ Mur chroniący Halabardników został zniszczony, \\textbf{nie są oni chronieni}.\n"
"  Złe Oczy atakują \\textbf{bez kary}.}}\n"
"\\newline\\newline"
